content: Signup Form Sign up for the Badgers Roundup Welcome to the Badgers Roundup, a weekly newsletter that captures your Brock University Badgers player and team news. * Email This is a required field. First Name Last Name Sign Up By submitting this form, you are consenting to receive marketing emails from: Brock University, 1812 Sir Sir Isaac Brock Way, St. Catharines, ON L2S 3A1, CA You can revoke your consent to receive emails at any time by using the SafeUnsubscribe® link, found at the bottom of every email. Emails are serviced by Constant Contact
